<h1>Orders</h1>

<div class="docbody">
<div class="opener">
<table class="password"><tr>
		<td class="parole">Parole: Loudon.</td>
		<td class="csigns"></td>
	      </tr></table>
<table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationRight">Winchester: Thursday, July 22d 1756.</td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
</div>
<p>Mr Gists waggon (and another, if it be found necessary) to be immediately loaded for Conogochieg,<a class="ptr" href="#GEWN-02-03-02-0257-fn-0001" id="GEWN-02-03-02-0257-fn-0001-ptr">1</a> with the following Things; videlicet:</p>
<table class="bodytext" id="Col03d246t1" style="margin-left: 1.5em;">
               <tr>
	      <td class="num" style="padding-right: 0.5em !important; text-align: right;">25</td>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap;">narrow axes</td>
	      <td class="num" style="padding-right: 0.5em !important; text-align: right;">2</td>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap;">Saw sets</td>
	    </tr>
               <tr>
	      <td class="num" style="padding-right: 0.5em !important; text-align: right;">6</td>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap;">broad ditto</td>
	      <td class="num" style="padding-right: 0.5em !important; text-align: right;">2</td>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap;">Carpenters adzes</td>
	    </tr>
               <tr>
	      <td class="num" style="padding-right: 0.5em !important; text-align: right;">4</td>
